title: 15 Minute Interval Training Treadmill Workout | Cardio & Strength to Burn Fat and Tone Up
description:
Can’t find the time to workout? We’ve created a quick 15-minute HIIT treadmill workout that can be modified to suit anyone. This easy to follow workout combines strength and cardio to make the most of your time by burning fat and toning simultaneously.
 
For the full written workout head to the blog: 
https://www.orbitfitness.com.au/blog/15-minute-interval-training-treadmill-workout 

Equipment links:
StarTrack ST25D.1 Treadmill https://www.orbitfitness.com.au/store/treadmills/startrack-treadmill-st25d1?sku=ST25D.1
Rubber Hex Dumbbells https://www.orbitfitness.com.au/store/weights/dumbbells/rubber-hex-dumbbells-rdch?sku=RDCH

https://www.orbitfitness.com.au/store/functional-training/orbit-micro-band-set-mini-strength-bands-oba6005?sku=OBA6005

Spotify Treadmill playlist: https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5g6Bn2ktpGUuCxjQP8IZ2T?si=ufvx9W7iQC2mZsxYeWiRjQ

CHAPTERS:
0:00 Workout run-down
03:08 Straight into the workout
20:52 Bonus ab round
26:31 Cool down
